## Quick Reference (bottom of context — intentional)

### Hunters
| Hunter  | HP  | Mana | Dodge           | Status | Signature Combo |
|---------|-----|------|-----------------|--------|-----------------|
| Dabik   | 80  | 120  | Blink           | Bleed  | L→L→H teleport behind |
| Benzu   | 160 | 70   | Shoulder Charge | Stun   | H→H→L AoE slam |
| Sereisa | 100 | 100  | Electric Dash   | Slow   | L→H→L chain lightning |
| Vesol   | 90  | 130  | Flame Scatter   | Burn   | L→L→L→H burn AoE |

### Input (P1 only until Phase 3)
Keyboard: WASD move | J light | K heavy | Shift dodge | E special | F interact | Esc pause
Gamepad: axes[0/1] move (dz 0.3) | btn0 interact | btn1 dodge | btn2 light | btn3 heavy | btn5 special

### Combat Feel
Light hitstop 80ms | Heavy hitstop 150ms | Dodge 300ms / 200ms i-frames
Every hit: sparks + screenshake + stagger | Enemy telegraph before every attack

### Phase Gates (do not build ahead)
| Phase | Unlocks |
|-------|---------|
| 1 | Core engine + combat input |
| 2 | Enemy AI + juice + combos + damage numbers + telegraphs |
| 3 | Hunter models + 4P input |
| 4 | Zones + bosses + screen transitions + boss intro + level clear |
| 5 | HUD + shop + XP |
| 6 | Audio + deploy |
